OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Ffine end to the day with some late
OL,7,Fsunshine but an increasing risk of
OL,8,Fshowers overnight, perhaps
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy and thundery
OL,10,Ftowards the end of the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,13,Fsome showery, perhaps thundery, rain
OL,14,Faround. Becoming brighter from the
OL,15,Fsouth through the afternoon but still
OL,16,Fsome showers around. Warm and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
