OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry,
OL,6,Fbright start Saturday but occasionally
OL,7,Fheavy rain spreads east in afternoon.
OL,8,FSunday and Monday look much cooler
OL,9,Fwith sunny spells and showers and an
OL,10,Foccasionally fresh southwesterly
OL,11,Fbreeze.
